Description:
When you realize you are inside a huge sand pit that slowly engulfs you towards the center.

Suddenly, a large sandworm appears from inside the pit. The worm opens its big toothy mouth and waits for the sand to drag you towards it.
DescriptionAction: It seems inevitable that you will have to defeat it if you don't want to be devoured.
